    vtrans:"abhayaṁ sattva-saṁśuddhir jñāna-yoga-vyavasthitiḥ",
    veng:"Fearlessness; purification of one's existence; cultivation of spiritual knowledge; charity; control of the senses; performance of sacrifice; study of the Vedas; austerity; simplicity; nonviolence; truthfulness; freedom from anger... these are the transcendental qualities of godly men.",
