    kid:"This is the MOST IMPORTANT verse of the whole Bhagavad Gita — out of 700 verses! Krishna said: 'Let go of everything — all your worrying, all your planning, all your fear — and just completely trust me. Give everything to me. I PROMISE I will take care of everything. DON'T BE AFRAID.' This is God's biggest and most beautiful promise to every single one of us, in every age.",
